Insider Activity


Individual




Andreas Rouvé



Dr. Andreas Rouve is President & Chief Executive Officer at Spectrum Brands, Inc., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. and President at Pile d'Alsace SAS. He  is on the Board of Directors at Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. Dr. Rouve was previously employed as CFO-Portable Batteries Division by VARTA AG and Finance Director by 3C Alliance LLP. He received his MBA from the University of Mannheim and a doctorate degree from Johannes Kepler Universit?t Linz.



